Short: RF Wattmeter, for use with WinUAE-ADC.
Uploader: wisecracker@tesco.net (Barry Walker).
Author: wisecracker@tesco.net (Barry Walker).
Type: hard/hack


Requires: 1) ~WinUAE-ADC.lha~ and ~WinUAE-ADC.readme~ from the ~hard/hack~
             drawer of ~AMINET~, plus all of the requirements inside of
             the ~WinUAE-ADC.lha~ archive.
          2) ~Project10~ of ~TestGear3.lha~ and ~TestGear3.readme~ from
             the ~hard/hack~ drawer of ~AMINET~.


Version: 1.00.00


Distribution: Emailware, (Freeware).

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

  Overview:-
  ----------

  This project is a port of the Radio Frequency Wattmeter, ~Project10~ of
  ~TestGear3.lha~ and ~TestGear3.readme~ from the ~hard/hack~ drawer of
  ~AMINET~. Although it works slightly differently it looks identical.

  The hardware to be built is identical and the calibration is, as per
  the ~Calibration_Info~ file from the ~WinUAE-RFW.lha~ archive.

