    Testing Evaluation.
    -------------------

    Designed primarily for Amiga Forever 5+ or better, WinUAE, (see above).
    (Windows 98 to) Windows XP and Amiga Forever 5+ or better.

    An A500+, an A600 with various memory configurations, the
    same A600 emulating WB3 with various memory configurations,
    an A1200 with various memory configurations.

    (Also tested on a 1MB old style AMIGA 500 with OS1.3x but uncalibrated.)

